      • doApply

        public final boolean doApply(LaubeRequestSystemAcceptor laubeRequestSystemAcceptor,
                             LaubeRequestSystemVisitor laubeRequestSystemVisitor)
                      throws LaubeException
        Make the application-based processing.
        パラメータ:
        laubeRequestSystemAcceptor - Application business data
        laubeVisitor - Pass the visitor. The application business can not be passed only visitor class to perform the application business. If you pass any other visitor class, an exception occurs.
        戻り値:
        Processing result
        例外:
        LaubeException
